00:00:12.370 --> 00:00:14.010
&gt;&gt; If you want to find out whether or not

00:00:14.010 --> 00:00:16.300
a trait is influenced more by genetics or more by

00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:18.210
environment, then you need to find a pair of people

00:00:18.210 --> 00:00:21.000
who are identical. And see if they both have that trait.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:22.410
&gt;&gt; So, you mean like twins.

